🏥 Insurance Claim Amount Prediction
📌 Project Overview

This project focuses on predicting medical insurance charges based on personal attributes that are age, BMI, smoking status. The goal is to build a regression model that can estimate healthcare costs and uncover the key factors influencing them.

🎯 Objective

* Predict insurance claim amounts using Linear Regression
* Analyze how features like age, BMI, and smoking habits affect medical costs
* Evaluate model performance using MAE (Mean Absolute Error) and RMSE (Root Mean Squared Error)

---

📂 Dataset

* Medical Cost Personal Dataset
* Features include:

  * Age
  * Sex
  * BMI (Body Mass Index)
  * children
  * Smoking status
  * Region
  * Charges (target variable)



